#

Spicy Korean Beef Tacos

$15
550 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

SoyEggs

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinDairy Free

Tags:

Asian FusionTacosQuick Meal

Description

Savory beef tacos with a spicy kick, topped with tangy kimchi and creamy Sriracha mayo.

Ingredients

  • Ground beef: 1 lb
  • Taco seasoning: 2 tbsp
  • Soy sauce: 2 tbsp
  • Corn tortillas: 8
  • Kimchi: 1 cup
  • Sriracha: 2 tbsp
  • Mayonnaise: 1/4 cup
  • Green onions: 2, sliced
  • Sesame seeds: 1 tbsp
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
